A cyberpunk-style digital illustration of a lone programmer seated at a curved workstation with multiple holographic displays floating in mid-air, each screen showing different streams of glowing code cascading downward in neon blue and magenta. The scene is set in a dark, moody room with rain-streaked windows revealing a futuristic cityscape of towering skyscrapers and flying vehicles. Translucent AI entities—abstract geometric forms with flowing wireframe bodies—hover around the programmer, each examining different holographic panels, some pointing at code sections, others conferring with each other in silent collaboration. Cables and fiber optic lines snake across the floor, pulsing with soft light. The programmer wears a sleek headset with a subtle glow, deeply focused. The atmosphere is electric yet contemplative, with dramatic rim lighting in cyan and purple casting long shadows, steam rising from a forgotten coffee cup nearby.
